---
title: FastAPI + Celery + Redis Sequence Diagram
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant FastAPI
    participant Redis
    participant Celery
    Client->>FastAPI: POST /heavy_task/
    FastAPI->>Redis: Send Task
    Celery->>Redis: Fetch Task
    Celery->>Celery: Execute Task
    Celery->>Redis: Store Result
    Client->>FastAPI: GET /tasks/{task_id}
    FastAPI->>Redis: Fetch Result
    FastAPI->>Client: Return Result
